-- BP Cancels Dividend for First Three Quarters of This Year
-- Will Kennedy
-- 2010-06-16T18:41:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-16/bp-cancels-dividend-for-first-three-quarters-of-year-amid-gulf-oil-spill.html

          
          
             BP Plc said it will cancel dividend
payments for the first three quarters of the year including the
previously announced first quarter dividend due on June 21.  
          
          


  


        